  "title": "Luxury Gold Client Advisor | MBS | Base salary + Fixed commission",
  "description": "<p>Step into the world of luxury and heritage, an iconic fine jewelry brand renowned for craftsmanship and timeless elegance. We are looking for passionate <strong>Client Advisors</strong> to deliver an exceptional luxury retail experience at our Marina Bay Sands boutique.</p><p>💰 <strong>Salary:</strong><br /><strong>$3,200 – $4,500 + Commission</strong></p><h3>💎 <strong>Your Role</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Deliver outstanding customer service and create a memorable luxury experience for every client</p></li><li><p>Assist customers in selecting high-quality jewelry and provide expert product advice</p></li><li><p>Build meaningful, long-term relationships to drive brand loyalty and repeat business</p></li><li><p>Achieve individual and team sales targets through service excellence</p></li><li><p>Maintain impeccable grooming and professionalism in line with luxury brand standards</p></li></ul><h3>✨ <strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Previous experience in retail or customer service</p></li><li><p>Applicants without retail experience but with a Cabin Crew / hospitality service background are welcome</p></li><li><p>Passion for luxury retail and representing a prestigious brand</p></li><li><p>Strong communication skills and a positive, team-oriented attitude</p></li><li><p>Confidence, elegance, and a service-driven mindset</p></li></ul><h3>📩 <strong>How to Apply</strong></h3><p>Send us your resume and a photo of yourself:</p><p><strong>Email: </strong><a href=\"mailto:deborah@crew.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>deborah@crew.sg</strong></a></p><p>Ho Yu Qing Deborah (R1104551)</p><p>Crew by HRnet | HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd | EA License: 24C2435</p>",
